<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Studio Airin — Fotografi Profesional Banjarmasin</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  :root {
    --bg: #0c0c0c;
    --bg-card: #141414;
    --white: #f2f0ec;
    --dim: #6e6b64;
    --rose: #c4727a;
    --rose-soft: rgba(196,114,122,0.1);
    --border: #1e1e1e;
    --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    --font-body: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
  }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow-x: hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  ::selection { background: var(--rose); color: #fff; }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
    background: rgba(12,12,12,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  }
  .logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .logo em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .nav-r { display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; }
  .nav-r a {
    color: var(--dim); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 400;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }
  .nav-r a:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .nav-cta-r {
    color: var(--rose) !important;
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,114,122,0.3);
    padding: 0.45rem 1.1rem; border-radius: 100px;
  }
  .nav-cta-r:hover { background: var(--rose-soft); }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 0 3rem 5rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 40%, var(--bg) 100%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1215 0%, #0c0c0c 50%, #0f1210 100%);
  }
  .hero-content { position: relative; }
  .hero-tag {
    font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    color: var(--rose); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.2s;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    line-height: 1.0; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.4s;
  }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .hero-row {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards 0.6s;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 380px; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .btn-rose {
    background: var(--rose); color: #fff;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem; border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn-rose:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(196,114,122,0.25); }

  /* GALLERY */
  .gallery { padding: 5rem 3rem; }
  .gallery-head {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .gallery-head h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .gallery-head h2 em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .gallery-filter {
    display: flex; gap: 1rem;
  }
  .gallery-filter span {
    font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--dim); cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.3s;
    padding-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .gallery-filter span.active {
    color: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rose);
  }
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: auto;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .g-item {
    border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;
    position: relative; cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.4s;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .g-item:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
  .g-item .g-inner {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .g-item:nth-child(1) .g-inner { aspect-ratio: 3/4; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1520, #0c0c0c); }
  .g-item:nth-child(2) .g-inner { aspect-ratio: 1; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a10, #0c0c0c); }
  .g-item:nth-child(3) .g-inner { aspect-ratio: 3/4; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10151a, #0c0c0c); }
  .g-item:nth-child(4) .g-inner { aspect-ratio: 4/3; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1015, #0c0c0c); }
  .g-item:nth-child(5) .g-inner { aspect-ratio: 4/3; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #151a10, #0c0c0c); }
  .g-item:nth-child(6) .g-inner { aspect-ratio: 1; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #15101a, #0c0c0c); }

  .g-overlay {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7) 0%, transparent 50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.4s;
  }
  .g-item:hover .g-overlay { opacity: 1; }
  .g-overlay h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 400;
  }
  .g-overlay span { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem; padding: 5rem 3rem; align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about-photo {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1215, #0c0c0c);
    border-radius: 300px 300px 12px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 5rem;
  }
  .about-text .sec-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--rose); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-text h2 em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services {
    padding: 5rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .svc-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .svc-item {
    background: var(--bg); padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .svc-item:hover { background: var(--bg-card); }
  .svc-item h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 400;
  }
  .svc-item p { color: var(--dim); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; }
  .svc-price {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--rose);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,114,122,0.2);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem; border-radius: 100px;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
  }
  .cta h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .cta h2 em { color: var(--rose); font-style: italic; }
  .cta p { color: var(--dim); max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; }
  .cta-glow {
    position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
    width: 400px; height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(196,114,122,0.06), transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(60px); pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--dim);
  }
  footer a { color: var(--dim); text-decoration: none; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--rose); }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(25px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-r { display: none; }
    .hero { padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .gallery { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .gallery-head { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; }
    .about { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-photo { aspect-ratio: 1; border-radius: 50%; max-width: 250px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .services { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .cta { padding: 5rem 1.5rem; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="logo">Studio <em>Airin</em></a>
  <div class="nav-r">
    <a href="#galeri">Galeri</a>
    <a href="#tentang">Tentang</a>
    <a href="#layanan">Layanan</a>
    <a href="#kontak" class="nav-cta-r">Booking</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <p class="hero-tag">📸 Fotografi Profesional — Banjarmasin</p>
    <h1>Setiap momen<br>punya <em>cerita</em></h1>
    <div class="hero-row">
      <p class="hero-desc">Mengabadikan momen berharga Anda dengan sentuhan artistik. Wedding, prewedding, produk, dan portrait.</p>
      <a href="#kontak" class="btn-rose">Booking Sesi →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="gallery" id="galeri">
  <div class="gallery-head reveal">
    <h2>Karya <em>Terbaru</em></h2>
    <div class="gallery-filter">
      <span class="active">Semua</span>
      <span>Wedding</span>
      <span>Portrait</span>
      <span>Produk</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="gallery-grid reveal">
    <div class="g-item">
      <div class="g-inner">💒</div>
      <div class="g-overlay"><h4>Wedding Rina & Adi</h4><span>Wedding</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="g-item">
      <div class="g-inner">👤</div>
      <div class="g-overlay"><h4>Corporate Portrait</h4><span>Portrait</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="g-item">
      <div class="g-inner">🌸</div>
      <div class="g-overlay"><h4>Prewedding Loksado</h4><span>Prewedding</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="g-item">
      <div class="g-inner">☕</div>
      <div class="g-overlay"><h4>Kopi Banua Catalog</h4><span>Produk</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="g-item">
      <div class="g-inner">👶</div>
      <div class="g-overlay"><h4>Newborn Session</h4><span>Portrait</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="g-item">
      <div class="g-inner">🎂</div>
      <div class="g-overlay"><h4>Birthday Party</h4><span>Event</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about" id="tentang">
  <div class="about-photo reveal">👩‍🎨</div>
  <div class="about-text reveal">
    <div class="sec-label">Tentang Saya</div>
    <h2>Airin — fotografer dengan mata untuk <em>detail</em></h2>
    <p>Sejak 2019, saya telah memotret lebih dari 200 sesi — dari wedding intimate hingga katalog produk UMKM. Berbasis di Banjarmasin, melayani seluruh Kalimantan Selatan.</p>
    <p>Setiap sesi bukan sekadar jepret. Saya percaya foto terbaik lahir dari koneksi — ketika subjek merasa nyaman, momen autentik muncul dengan sendirinya.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services" id="layanan">
  <div class="sec-label reveal" style="color:var(--rose);font-size:0.7rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.2em;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Paket Layanan</div>
  <h2 class="reveal" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3rem);margin-bottom:3rem;">Pilih sesuai <em style='color:var(--rose);font-style:italic;'>kebutuhan</em> Anda</h2>
  <div class="svc-row reveal">
    <div class="svc-item">
      <h3>Wedding</h3>
      <p>Dokumentasi full-day, 200+ foto edited, 1 album premium, video highlight 3 menit.</p>
      <span class="svc-price">Mulai Rp 5.000.000</span>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-item">
      <h3>Prewedding</h3>
      <p>1 lokasi, 2 jam sesi, 50+ foto edited, outfit guidance, lokasi Kalsel pilihan.</p>
      <span class="svc-price">Mulai Rp 2.500.000</span>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-item">
      <h3>Produk & UMKM</h3>
      <p>Foto produk katalog, flatlay, lifestyle. 20 foto per sesi. Cocok untuk online shop.</p>
      <span class="svc-price">Mulai Rp 500.000</span>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-item">
      <h3>Portrait</h3>
      <p>Personal, corporate, atau keluarga. Studio atau outdoor. 15+ foto edited.</p>
      <span class="svc-price">Mulai Rp 350.000</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta" id="kontak">
  <div class="cta-glow"></div>
  <h2 class="reveal">Punya momen yang<br>ingin <em>diabadikan?</em></h2>
  <p class="reveal">Konsultasi gratis. Saya bantu pilihkan paket yang tepat untuk Anda.</p>
  <a href="#" class="btn-rose reveal" style="font-size:1rem;padding:1rem 2.5rem;">
    📸 Chat WhatsApp
  </a>
</section>

<footer>
  <span>© 2026 Studio Airin. Banjarmasin, Kalimantan Selatan.</span>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:1.5rem;">
    <a href="#">Instagram</a>
    <a href="#">WhatsApp</a>
    <a href="#">TikTok</a>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  const reveals = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
  const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach(e => { if(e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });
  reveals.forEach(el => obs.observe(el));
</script>
</body>
</html>
